body { padding-top: 0px; font-family: "Fira Sans", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }h4 { font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; }code { font-family: Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Courier, monospace; }pre { font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 16px; background: rgb(247, 247, 247); border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 0px; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; }table { background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); }pre code { font-family: Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Courier, monospace; padding: 0px; }canvas { background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); cursor: pointer; }.well { margin-top: 75px; margin-bottom: 0px; }.navbar-inverse .navbar-brand { color: rgb(255, 255, 255); }.banner { background-color: rgb(0, 191, 136); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 25px 0px 35px; }.banner p, .banner-alt p { font-size: 18px; }.banner a { color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(255, 255, 255); }.banner-alt { background-color: rgb(238, 241, 244); color: rgb(107, 112, 124); padding: 25px 0px 35px; }.banner-alt h2 { color: rgb(85, 85, 85); }.home-list { list-style: none; font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 35px 0px; padding-left: 0px; line-height: 28px; }li.header { font-weight: bold; list-style: none; }.home-list > li { margin-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; }.home-list > li:last-child { border-bottom: 0px; }.home-list > li > ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0px; }.home-list > li > ul > li { font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); }.home-list > li > ul > li > a { font-weight: normal; }.content-container { margin-top: 35px; }#query-form { border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); padding: 10px; }.action-focus.focus { border: 5px solid orange; }.action-blur.error { border: 5px solid red; }.action-div, .rightclick-action-div { cursor: pointer; }.action-opacity { position: relative; margin-top: 50px; }.action-opacity .opacity-cover { text-align: center; line-height: 50px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px; position: absolute; top: -5px; left: -5px; width: 235px; height: 60px; background-color: red; opacity: 0.7; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 2px 7px; }.utlity-jquery li.active { background-color: rgb(0, 104, 162); color: white; }.network-btn, .network-post, .network-put { margin-bottom: 20px; }#scroll-horizontal, #scroll-vertical, #scroll-both, #scrollable-horizontal, #scrollable-vertical, #scrollable-both { background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border: 1px solid rgb(119, 119, 119); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 15px; }#scrollable-horizontal ul, #scrollable-vertical ul, #scrollable-both ul { padding: 0px; overflow: auto; }#scrollable-horizontal ul > li, #scrollable-vertical ul > li, #scrollable-both ul > li { list-style: none; margin: 20px; float: left; }#scrollable-horizontal ul > li { display: inline-block; }::-webkit-scrollbar { appearance: none; width: 12px; height: 12px; }::-webkit-scrollbar-track { box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 0px 6px inset; border-radius: 4px; }::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5) 0px 0px 6px inset; }.hljs { display: block; overflow-x: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(247, 247, 247); }.hljs-comment, .hljs-quote { color: rgb(153, 153, 153); }.hljs-keyword, .hljs-selector-tag, .hljs-subst { color: rgb(29, 117, 179); font-weight: normal; }.hljs-number, .hljs-literal, .hljs-variable, .hljs-template-variable, .hljs-tag .hljs-attr { color: rgb(0, 134, 179); font-weight: normal; }.hljs-string, .hljs-doctag { color: rgb(24, 54, 145); }.hljs-title, .hljs-section, .hljs-selector-id { color: rgb(153, 0, 0); font-weight: normal; }.hljs-subst { font-weight: normal; }.hljs-type, .hljs-class .hljs-title { color: rgb(68, 85, 136); font-weight: normal; }.hljs-tag, .hljs-name, .hljs-attribute { color: rgb(0, 0, 128); font-weight: normal; }.hljs-regexp, .hljs-link { color: rgb(0, 153, 38); }.hljs-symbol, .hljs-bullet { color: rgb(153, 0, 115); }.hljs-built_in, .hljs-builtin-name { color: rgb(0, 134, 179); }.hljs-meta { color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-weight: normal; }.hljs-deletion { background: rgb(255, 221, 221); }.hljs-addition { background: rgb(221, 255, 221); }.hljs-emphasis { font-style: normal; }.hljs-strong { font-weight: normal; }

childNodes.textContent: This is an example app used to showcase
End-to-End (E2E) testing. For a full reference of our documentation, go to
Commands drive your tests in the browser like a real user would. They let you perform actions like typing, clicking, xhr requests, and can also assert things like "my button should be disabled".
Utilities give you access to methods from other commonly used libraries.
The Cypress API enables you to configure the behavior of how Cypress works internally. You can do things like access Environment Variables, change configuration, create custom commands, and more.
